<h2 align="center">Instructions</h2>

<p>Welcome to the Miami University Sports Medicine Intranet. Please
fill out the forms you were instructed to in your welcome letter. The
steps for each form are:</p>

<ol>

<li>Select the form in the drop-down list and click the "Fill Out New
Form" button.</li>

<li>Fill out the form completely and click the "Submit" button at the
bottom of the page.</li>

<li>If you are a <font color="#a00000"><b>Veteran Student-Athlete</b></font>
or a <font color="#a00000"><b>Freshmen/Transfer Student - Athlete</b></font>
then please fill out the appropriate forms listed/assigned below:

<table align="center" border="0"><tr>
<td valign="top"><font color="#a00000"><b>Veteran Student-Athlete:
<ol>
<li>Athlete Release Form</li>
<li>FERPA Release Form</li>
<li>Health Appraisal Form</li>
<li>Health Information Release Form</li>
<li>Insurance Form</li>
<li>Waiver Form</li>
</ol>
</b></font>
</td>

<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>

<td valign="top"><font color="#a00000"><b>Freshmen/Transfer Student-Athlete:
<ol>
<li>Athlete Release Form</li>
<li>FERPA Release</li>
<li>Health Appraisal Form</li>
<li>Health Information Release Form</li>
<li>Insurance Form</li>
<li>Waiver Form</li>
<li>Family History Form</li>
<li>Health History Form</li>
</ol>
</b></font>
</td>

</tr></table>
</li>

<li>If you see a message stating "Form could not be submitted due to
the following reasons:", then please read the warnings/errors listed
in red and make the appropriate corrections on the form. Then click
the "Submit" button at the bottom of the page.</li>

<li>Once the form has passed verification, you will be asked to review
it. Please double check all of your responses then click the "Insert
Form Data into Database" button at the bottom of the page. If you
would like to change any of the information, then click on the "Edit
Form" button instead.</li>

<li>If successful, then you will see a message stating that the
"Database insertion was successful".</li>

<li>To see the updated list of completed forms, click on the "Refresh
Form List" link at the top of the page.</li>

<li>To modify a form after it is submitted, click on the form in your
list and click the "Modify" button at the bottom of the form.  Please
note that you may make modifications to your information only during
the designated time that you have access to the system.</li>

<li>Once forms have all <font color="#a00000"><b>FINAL</b></font>
modifications to them, please <font
color="#a00000"><b>PRINT</b></font> each form off and <font
color="#a00000"><b>SIGN/DATE</b></font> in all the appropriate places
(if you are under the age of 18 please have your legal guardian/parent
sign in all the appropriate places).  To print a form, click on it in
your list of forms, then click the "Print" link at the bottom of the
form.</li>

<li>After forms are <font color="#a00000"><b>PRINTED</b></font> and
<font color="#a00000"><b>SIGNED/DATED</b></font> please mail them to
or drop them off at:

<table align="center" border="0"><tr>
<td>Miami University Sports Medicine<br>
Attn: Mr. Gale Newton<br>
144 Yager Stadium<br>
Oxford, OH 45056<br>
</td>
</tr></table>
</li>

</ol>

<p>If you have problems or questions, please contact Jennifer
Beardslee at beardsjm@muohio.edu or call at 513-529-4777.</p>

